title.rendered: WESTERN FILTERS Volkswagen Amarok 2017-on 3.0L V6 TDi550 – Mann PreLine-Plus Diesel Prefilter Kit PL643DPK

content.rendered:
Mann PreLine 150
PreLine-Plus Diesel Prefilter Kit suits:
Volkswagen Amarok 2017-on 3.0L V6 TDi550

Cross Reference: PL150DP 1809 / PL643DPK / DP09K

MANN+HUMMEL PreLine Prefilter Series:
Reduces the contamination level of fuel already upstream of the pre-feed pump in the low pressure circuit. In addition, the Multigrade F filter media separate more than 93 percent of any water in the fuel and therefore meet the requirements of leading manufacturers of injection systems. The perfect interaction between the PreLine prefilter and the MANN+HUMMEL main filter offers maximum protection for the sensitive injection system and contributes to the economic running of your engine. Main Features & Advantages: For use with diesel fuel DIN ISO 590 (5% FAME) DIN 51 628 (7% FAME) kerosene JET-A1 :: For volume flow rates up to 150 l/h :: Use of ‘multigrade high performance’ media :: 93% water separation :: Modular system for excellent flexibility :: Easy handling during servicing :: Integrated and effective hand pump with 45° position to drain off water and for priming during service :: Integrated water collector :: Parallel operation possible with a number of systems

PreLine 150 Specifications:
Comes with a Single Head offering variable connection possibilities Robust design in different sizes Designed for easy servicing Spin-on filter.
Head Connection Thread: M16 x 1.5
Head Length: 163mm / Head Outr.Diam: 76mm
Spin-on Filter: PL 150 / Nominal Flow Rate: 150
Water Separation: >93%
Operating Pressure: 4
Dimensions: 98 x 102 x 247mm

For additional Information: MANN PreLine 150 >
